  "keyFeatures": [
    "AI-powered CHORUS scheduler: submodular optimization assigns targets to telescope nodes based on predicted photometric information gain",
    "Automated photometry pipeline: ASTAP plate solve → comparison stars → aperture photometry → AAVSO submission",
    "Node agent: cross-platform Python daemon controlling Seestar telescopes via ALPACA API with FSEvents/inotify image watching",
    "Claude-powered weight tuning monitor with backtest gate for observability scoring weights",
    "Flutter member app (iOS, Android, web/PWA) with accessibility-first design (VoiceOver, TalkBack, haptics, sonification)",
    "Multi-source alert ingestion: ALeRCE, ATLAS, ASAS-SN, AAVSO, Gaia, TNS",
    "Reliability ledger: per-node Beta posteriors for p_exec, p_accept, kappa (hardware-normalized precision skill)",
    "Cross-platform installer system: NSIS (Windows), .pkg (macOS), systemd (Linux)",
    "Node activation code system linking member accounts to telescope hardware",
    "Interactive marketing site with live network stats, Aladin Lite sky visualization"
  ],
